Description: The bar theme for [xonsh shell](https://xon.sh).
        
        ## Install
        ```
        xpip install -U git+https://github.com/anki-code/xontrib-prompt-bar
        echo 'xontrib load prompt_bar' >> ~/.xonshrc
        # Reload xonsh
        ```
        
